1
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:24,440
{\an8}[Karya ini disarankan bagi penonton berumur 18 tahun ke atas]

2
00:00:24,460 --> 00:00:25,870
{\an8}[Semua plot dalam karya ini hanya fiksyen, jangan meniru dalam kehidupan sebenar]
{\an8}[Penonton di bawah umur 18 tahun, sila menonton bersama penjaga]

3
00:00:29,140 --> 00:00:31,750
{\an8}[Bumi, negara S]

4
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,100
Dah terlambat.

5
00:01:02,220 --> 00:01:03,220
Di mana orang itu?

6
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,980
Tak nampak, kenapa?

7
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:07,670
Dia dah hilang.

8
00:01:06,930 --> 00:01:08,210
{\an8}[Perpustakaan]

9
00:01:19,090 --> 00:01:20,620
Mereka dah pergi cari awak.

10
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:26,750
Siapa awak?

11
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:35,140
Cepat lari.

12
00:01:40,670 --> 00:01:41,949
Lari sehingga hujung koridor,

13
00:01:41,950 --> 00:01:42,610
belok kiri.

14
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:44,259
Kemudian?

15
00:01:44,289 --> 00:01:46,020
Pintu pertama di sebelah kiri.

16
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:47,940
Buka pintu.

17
00:01:50,030 --> 00:01:51,030
Tak dapat dibuka.

18
00:02:00,130 --> 00:02:01,350
Macam mana sekarang?

19
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,699
Di belakang awak.

20
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,300
{\an8}[Panggilan yang tak diketahui]

21
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,078
- Jom pergi tonton filem.
- Okey.

22
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,480
Kenapa dengan orang ini?

23
00:03:05,950 --> 00:03:06,540
Serang!

24
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:24,660
Di mana Shen Yao?

25
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:02,830
Nampaknya,

26
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,440
kita tiada pilihan lagi.

27
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:08,330
Tak,

28
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:10,290
awak yang tiada pilihan!

29
00:04:12,110 --> 00:04:14,410
Awak akan menanggung akibat yang teruk.

30
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,610
Gaya nampak hebat,

31
00:04:26,910 --> 00:04:27,630
tapi...

32
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:03,460
Memang menyusahkan.

33
00:05:06,170 --> 00:05:08,770
Bukan mudah untuk mulakan penjelmaan semula.

34
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:11,580
Apa?

35
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,090
Jangan bergurau lagi!

36
00:05:25,090 --> 00:05:27,090
Awak tak dapat buat apa-apa di sini.

37
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,420
Harap penjelmaan semula kali ini...

38
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:48,370
Akan ada pengakhiran yang berbeza.

39
00:05:48,970 --> 00:05:49,570
Shen Yao.

40
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:51,970
Shen Yao.

41
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:55,780
Xiaoxiu?

42
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:57,769
Tak sangka awak curi tulang di sini.

43
00:05:57,770 --> 00:05:58,919
Ada satu soalan yang saya tak reti buat,

44
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,320
awak tolong saya tengok.

45
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:01,630
Baiklah.

46
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,880
Jom, saya pergi tengok.

47
00:06:32,890 --> 00:06:37,350
♪ Jika dapat larikan diri daripada takdir yang ditentukan ♪

48
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:42,250
♪ Apabila menyentuh kebenaran masa dan ruang, rahsia yang paling utama ♪

49
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:47,460
♪ Membangkitkan takdir yang melampaui kebiasaan ini ♪

50
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:50,420
♪ Membangunkan diri yang lain ♪

51
00:06:51,210 --> 00:06:56,169
♪ Pandangan matamu yang paling jernih dan tabah ♪

52
00:06:56,170 --> 00:07:00,420
♪ Kristal yang dipenuhi dengan kekuatan tanpa batas ♪

53
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,919
♪ Lepaskan sifat semula jadiku ♪

54
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:06,000
♪ Mengekstrak setiap nafas dengan laju ♪

55
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,000
♪ Keadilan yang bersinar ♪

56
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:12,460
♪ Satu-satunya kebenaran dalam pertarungan ♪

57
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:15,000
♪ Kamu semua dapat dengar jeritanku sekarang ♪

58
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:17,500
♪ Walaupun kehidupanku pernah penuh dengan kekesalan ♪

59
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,220
♪ Buka semula ♪

60
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:20,540
♪ Berusaha, berjuang dan berlatih ♪

61
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:22,500
♪ Menemui masa depan ♪

62
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:24,870
♪ Jangan hanya berangan-angan, bertindaklah ♪

63
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:27,500
♪ Dengan semangat keberanian, tiada apa-apa yang dapat menewaskan aku ♪

64
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:32,120
♪ Tubuh hancur berkecai demi melindungi kelembutanmu ♪

65
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:36,250
♪ Enggan menunduk lagi ♪

66
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:42,560
{\an8}[Episod 1]
{\an8}[Super Cube]

67
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:44,740
Mari minum!

68
00:07:54,210 --> 00:07:54,810
Habislah.

69
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,200
Susahnya,

70
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,670
saya kalah lagi.

71
00:07:58,170 --> 00:07:59,100
Terima hukuman,

72
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:01,389
sampai giliran awak untuk jawab soalan.

73
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:02,010
Shen Yao,

74
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:04,450
untuk soalan kebenaran yang awak cabut,

75
00:08:04,890 --> 00:08:06,890
sebutkan nama orang yang awak suka.

76
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:10,219
Wang Xiaoxiu, awak begitu teruja.

77
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:12,959
Jangan-jangan awak sangka Shen Yao menyukai awak?

78
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:13,820
Tak!

79
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,790
Walaupun saya dah lama kenal Yao,

80
00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:18,910
masih belum sampai tahap suka.

81
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:20,540
Apa yang saya cakap ini?

82
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:23,550
Yao, malah panggil nama dengan begitu mesra.

83
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:24,819
Jangan risau,

84
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:27,199
perempuan takkan menyukai lelaki macam jenis awak ini,

85
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,660
apatah lagi Shen Yao.

86
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:32,109
Perempuan suka lelaki yang tampan dan bergaya macam saya.

87
00:08:32,110 --> 00:08:33,260
Jangan mimpi!

88
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,159
Kamu jangan fikir lagi.

89
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,799
Hanya lelaki berkualiti yang sepadan dengan Yao,

90
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:39,820
betul tak?

91
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,640
Yao boleh beritahu kami secara rahsia.

92
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:44,070
Saya mesti cakap?

93
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:46,070
Tentulah, mestilah.

94
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,810
Ini terlalu memalukan.

95
00:08:49,090 --> 00:08:50,620
Sejak kecil hingga dewasa,

96
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:53,820
rasanya saya tak pernah cakap perkataan itu.

97
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:02,020
Awak mesti jujur.

98
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:09,580
Lelaki yang saya suka

99
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:11,640
ialah...

100
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,750
Wang... Wang Xiaoxiu.

101
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,170
Bukan saya?

102
00:09:18,410 --> 00:09:19,770
Janganlah bergurau.

103
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:21,870
Ini memang gurauan besar.

104
00:09:23,770 --> 00:09:24,930
Saya tak bergurau.

105
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:26,920
Sejak sekolah rendah,

106
00:09:27,650 --> 00:09:29,169
saya dah memerhatikannya.

107
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,160
Saya...

108
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:32,869
Tak sangka Yao meluahkan perasaan cinta terhadap saya.

109
00:09:32,870 --> 00:09:34,540
Rupa-rupanya, perasaan cinta...

110
00:09:34,410 --> 00:09:44,660
{\an8}[Aksi berbahaya, jangan meniru]

111
00:09:34,850 --> 00:09:36,310
Sakitnya.

112
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:39,470
Budak tak guna, berani awak rampas wanita abang!

113
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,250
Awak dah bosan hidup, kan?

114
00:09:41,780 --> 00:09:43,210
Pungguk rindukan bulan.

115
00:09:43,690 --> 00:09:46,079
Percaya tak saya akan campak awak untuk berikan makan kepada ikan sekarang?

116
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,489
- Entahlah siapa yang bocorkan rahsia
- Budak tak guna.

117
00:09:48,490 --> 00:09:50,719
sampai saya ditangkap dan dipisit oleh samseng Geng Utara Bandar.

118
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,410
Ber... bertenang, abang.

119
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,919
Bincang elok-elok kalau ada apa-apa.

120
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:54,810
Bincang?

121
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:55,970
Bincang apa?

122
00:09:56,690 --> 00:09:58,099
Semasa awak merampas wanita abang saya,

123
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,009
kenapa awak tak tahu berbincang pula?

124
00:09:59,010 --> 00:10:00,170
Dia ialah Sun Jun,

125
00:10:00,570 --> 00:10:01,939
seorang samseng yang terkenal,

126
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,200
pemikat hati Shen Yao.

127
00:10:03,340 --> 00:10:03,870
Bukan,

128
00:10:04,310 --> 00:10:05,699
salah seorang pengacau.

129
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:07,810
Saya rasa awak ini memang berani.

130
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,409
Tak payah cakap banyak dengan dia lagi,

131
00:10:09,410 --> 00:10:11,740
campak dia dan berikan makan kepada ikan.

132
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,060
Yao,

133
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:15,430
dah lama tak jumpa.

134
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:17,300
Sun Jun?

135
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:19,549
Bukankah ini nombor telefon Xiaoxiu?

136
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,380
Di mana dia?

137
00:10:20,780 --> 00:10:22,739
Yao, jangan letakkan panggilan dulu.

138
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:25,529
Biar saya tunjukkan satu siaran langsung yang menarik kepada awak.

139
00:10:25,530 --> 00:10:28,810
Tengok, si miang yang mengganggu awak berada di sana.

140
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:29,410
Xiaoxiu?

141
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:31,210
Jangan libatkan Yao!

142
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:32,670
Ini hal kita berdua!

143
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,530
Berani awak lawan cakap lagi!

144
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,110
Xiaoxiu!

145
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:39,670
Jangan begitu cemas.

146
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:42,150
Saya hanya nak berbual dengan dia.

147
00:10:43,130 --> 00:10:44,870
Mari, Wang Xiaoxiu.

148
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:48,470
Cakaplah, siapa yang layak bersama dengan Shen Yao?

149
00:10:48,830 --> 00:10:50,690
Sun Jun, cepat lepaskan Xiaoxiu!

150
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,830
Fikirkan baik-baik dan teliti.

151
00:10:55,340 --> 00:10:58,229
Lagipun, ini hal penting yang berkaitan dengan nyawa.

152
00:10:58,230 --> 00:11:01,360
Awak begitu pandai, awak pasti tahu jawapannya.

153
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,310
Sun Jun!

154
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:03,160
Sun Jun,

155
00:11:04,210 --> 00:11:06,810
awak langsung tak layak memikat hati Shen Yao.

156
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,420
Kamu semua sampah!

157
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:18,330
Xiaoxiu!

158
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:22,059
Budak ini memang cari nahas!

159
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:23,889
Awak pun sama, berani awak lepaskan tangan!

160
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:26,339
Saya... saya pun tak tahu dia akan langgar saya.

161
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:27,870
Wang Xiaoxiu!

162
00:11:28,050 --> 00:11:30,510
Jangan berpura-pura mati, cepat terapung!

163
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:32,300
Tiada reaksi lagi, bos.

164
00:11:32,570 --> 00:11:33,430
Macam mana ini?

165
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:36,720
Kalau saya tak dapat melindungi cinta sendiri,

166
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,370
apa maknanya saya hidup?

167
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,720
Lelaki yang saya suka

168
00:11:41,450 --> 00:11:42,620
ialah Wang Xiaoxiu.

169
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:56,360
Saya sangka Wang Xiaoxiu sangat hebat.

170
00:11:56,410 --> 00:11:58,140
Rupa-rupanya, dia si cengeng.

171
00:11:58,170 --> 00:12:00,470
Yalah, dia lari begitu laju tadi.

172
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:25,670
Xiaoxiu.

173
00:12:27,060 --> 00:12:28,040
Shen Yao?

174
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:29,860
Awak tak bawa payung?

175
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:33,989
Jom kita balik rumah bersama-sama.

176
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:34,510
Tak.

177
00:12:38,310 --> 00:12:40,599
Awak bersembunyi di sini kerana tak nak bertugas, kan?

178
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,510
Bukan.

179
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,679
Saya boleh balik rumah sendiri.

180
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,750
{\an8}[Sekolah Rendah Eksperimen]

181
00:12:44,810 --> 00:12:47,240
Tapi hujan sekarang.

182
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:48,330
{\an8}[Klinik Pergigian]

183
00:12:49,730 --> 00:12:52,220
Tak apa, tunggu hujan berhenti baru pergi.

184
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,409
Xiaoxiu, lengan awak berdarah.

185
00:12:56,410 --> 00:12:57,410
Biar saya tengok.

186
00:12:57,740 --> 00:12:59,010
Tak... tak perlu!

187
00:12:59,210 --> 00:13:00,310
Biar saya tengok,

188
00:13:00,570 --> 00:13:02,619
mungkin awak akan sembuh dengan lebih cepat.

189
00:13:02,620 --> 00:13:03,680
Kenapa awak malu?

190
00:13:04,070 --> 00:13:06,530
Sejak bila dia menjadi begitu lemah lembut?

191
00:13:17,420 --> 00:13:18,410
Shen Yao.

192
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:20,810
Terima kasih.

193
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:22,810
Hujan dah berhenti.

194
00:13:23,230 --> 00:13:25,230
Jom kita balik rumah bersama-sama.

195
00:13:34,820 --> 00:13:35,900
Macam ada cahaya.

196
00:13:37,170 --> 00:13:38,070
Apa itu?

197
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:56,770
Panasnya!

198
00:13:57,300 --> 00:13:58,500
Apa yang berlaku ini?

199
00:13:58,970 --> 00:14:01,300
Ia seolah-olah masuk ke dalam badan saya.

200
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,460
Apa ini?

201
00:14:17,420 --> 00:14:18,530
Ini...

202
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:21,090
Saya hampir mati lemas!

203
00:14:22,130 --> 00:14:23,200
Saya dah mati?

204
00:14:24,940 --> 00:14:26,169
Di mana saya sekarang?

205
00:14:26,170 --> 00:14:28,030
Saya diculik oleh makhluk asing?

206
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:29,400
Tuan perumah,

207
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:31,669
awak boleh melukis satu lingkungan teleportasi

208
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:34,070
dengan jejari 15 meter berpusat pada saya.

209
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,569
Selepas itu, awak akan dihantar

210
00:14:36,570 --> 00:14:39,919
ke mana-mana titik koordinat dalam lingkungan teleportasi itu.

211
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:40,570
Apa?

212
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:49,010
Saya akan terjatuh dan mati!

213
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:50,630
Cepat cari!

214
00:14:51,540 --> 00:14:53,740
Tak sangka mereka tengah mencari saya.

215
00:14:54,770 --> 00:14:56,970
Jangan balik rumah kalau tak jumpa dia!

216
00:15:00,290 --> 00:15:02,179
Kamu dengar tak apa-apa bunyi tadi?

217
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:04,270
Bos, adakah awak berhalusinasi?

218
00:15:05,250 --> 00:15:06,019
Jangan cakap banyak!

219
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:06,589
Cepat cari!

220
00:15:06,590 --> 00:15:07,930
Baik.

221
00:15:08,210 --> 00:15:09,210
Peliknya.

222
00:15:09,850 --> 00:15:12,780
Jelas sekali saya rasa ada seseorang di atas langit.

223
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:17,570
Sakit... sakitnya.

224
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:19,440
Kenapa saya balik ke kelas lagi?

225
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:20,909
Saya diteleportasikan?

226
00:15:20,910 --> 00:15:21,789
Apa yang berlaku?

227
00:15:21,790 --> 00:15:22,579
Kuasa psikik?

228
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:23,460
Tuan perumah,

229
00:15:23,610 --> 00:15:26,969
awak telah melancarkan teleportasi ruang secara rawak berulang kali.

230
00:15:26,970 --> 00:15:28,430
Ada bunyi dalam otak saya.

231
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:29,610
Dalam badan awak.

232
00:15:30,430 --> 00:15:31,540
Dalam badan saya?

233
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:33,770
Di mana? Menjijikkan betul!

234
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,710
Telefon bimbit saya.

235
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,690
Jadi, siapa awak sebenarnya?

236
00:15:38,710 --> 00:15:39,710
Ada orang datang.

237
00:15:39,930 --> 00:15:40,450
Siapa?

238
00:15:53,370 --> 00:15:54,509
Apa yang berlaku ini?

239
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,910
Lantai penuh dengan air.

240
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,680
Yao?

241
00:16:01,790 --> 00:16:02,740
{\an8}[Shen Yao]

242
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,080
Itu...

243
00:16:05,110 --> 00:16:06,329
Akhirnya awak jawab panggilan!

244
00:16:06,330 --> 00:16:07,330
Awak tak apa-apa?

245
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:09,200
Saya sangka awak dah mati.

246
00:16:09,250 --> 00:16:10,210
Di mana awak?

247
00:16:10,470 --> 00:16:11,310
Di rumah.

248
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:14,429
Dah sampai rumah pun tak beritahu saya,

249
00:16:14,430 --> 00:16:15,600
saya sangat risau.

250
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:17,440
Saya sangat terkejut tadi.

251
00:16:18,370 --> 00:16:19,639
Mereka terlalu melampau kali ini,

252
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,640
lebih baik kita buat laporan polis.

253
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:23,059
Jangan tergesa-gesa.

254
00:16:23,060 --> 00:16:24,039
Saya agak cerdik,

255
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:26,009
saya berenang balik semasa kekecohan.

256
00:16:26,010 --> 00:16:28,540
Mungkin mereka masih mencari saya di tebing.

257
00:16:29,570 --> 00:16:30,970
Awak masih boleh ketawa?

258
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:32,940
Baiklah, masa dah lewat.

259
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:35,299
Banyak perkara dah berlaku hari ini.

260
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:36,160
Rehatlah awal.

261
00:16:36,670 --> 00:16:37,510
Tunggu!

262
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:47,969
Pasti tiada sesiapa akan percaya kalau ceritakan apa yang berlaku hari ini.

263
00:16:47,970 --> 00:16:49,700
Yao juga tak boleh dilibatkan.

264
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:52,800
Tuan perumah,

265
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:54,510
awak dah bertenang?

266
00:16:56,540 --> 00:16:57,919
Kenapa awak berada di rumah saya?

267
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:00,520
Saya pernah kata saya berada dalam badan awak.

268
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:06,030
Lagi.

269
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,160
Selamat kembali.

270
00:17:12,740 --> 00:17:13,740
Sakitnya.

271
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:18,469
Kenapa saya masuk ke dalam ruang ini lagi?

272
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:20,930
Siapa tuan perumah yang awak sebutkan tadi?

273
00:17:21,010 --> 00:17:24,439
Saya telah membina hubungan fizikal yang stabil dengan awak.

274
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:27,659
Jadi, awak telah dipilih sebagai saya, sistem muktamad alam semesta,

275
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:29,260
pengguna Kiub Hera.

276
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:31,590
Dengan kata-kata makhluk bumi,

277
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:33,240
awak ialah tuan saya.

278
00:17:33,670 --> 00:17:34,840
Kalau awak tak suka,

279
00:17:35,010 --> 00:17:36,809
awak boleh gunakan gelaran lain.

280
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:38,740
Apa sistem muktamad alam semesta?

281
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:41,859
Saya dah jemu dengar perkataan chunibyo sebegini sejak sekolah rendah.

282
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:43,220
Di mana ini sebenarnya?

283
00:17:43,570 --> 00:17:45,909
Rupa luaran saya di dunia fizik makroskopik

284
00:17:45,910 --> 00:17:48,209
ialah sebuah kiub sebesar tiga sentimeter persegi,

285
00:17:48,210 --> 00:17:52,270
tapi bahagian dalaman ialah ruang peribadi sebesar tiga meter persegi.

286
00:17:53,770 --> 00:17:55,870
Tempat ini kelihatan menarik.

287
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:08,640
Jadi,

288
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:11,609
saya tiba-tiba teleportasi ke sana sini juga

289
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:12,810
angkara awak?

290
00:18:12,970 --> 00:18:13,970
Analisis tepat.

291
00:18:16,340 --> 00:18:18,210
Kiub, kenapa awak bantu saya?

292
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:21,710
Demi merealisasikan hasrat awak

293
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:24,210
dan menjadi Raja Dunia.

294
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:34,850
Awak hanya perlu menggunakan sinaran gelombang mikro untuk mengesan,

295
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:39,180
{\an8}[Pratonton episod seterusnya]

296
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:37,619
maka awak boleh nampak semua objek dalam lingkungan itu.

297
00:18:37,620 --> 00:18:39,080
Sinaran gelombang mikro?

298
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,540
Dari mana awak datang?

299
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:45,390
Wang Xiaoxiu ada di sini tak?

300
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:47,289
Habislah, Sun Jun dah cari sampai ke sini.

301
00:18:47,290 --> 00:18:48,500
Yao, jangan takut.

302
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,600
Awak kata awak sistem super.

303
00:18:51,710 --> 00:18:52,910
Siapa pencipta awak?

304
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,910
Tuan, tiada hasil pencarian.

305
00:18:56,080 --> 00:18:58,860
Awak terlepas semalam, awak bernasib baik.

306
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:01,860
Hari ini, awak tak dapat lepaskan diri.

307
00:19:01,870 --> 00:19:05,000
Xiaoxiu, kenapa awak letakkan panggilan saya semalam?

308
00:19:05,330 --> 00:19:07,619
Bagaimana untuk meningkatkan kuasa psikik ini?

309
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:09,459
Sistem mempunyai fungsi penaiktarafan terbina dalam.

310
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,079
Hanya dengan menyerap permata bertenaga,

311
00:19:11,080 --> 00:19:12,680
kuasa akan terus meningkat.

312
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:31,570
♪ Adakah graviti bumi juga tertarik denganmu?♪

313
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:35,990
♪ Kau mula menjadi mempesonakan dalam kalangan orang ramai ♪

314
00:19:36,010 --> 00:19:41,950
♪ Kenapa aku tiba-tiba rasa begini?♪

315
00:19:44,610 --> 00:19:48,740
♪ Kenapa kau selalu muncul ♪

316
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:51,530
♪ Pada saat aku paling memerlukanmu ♪

317
00:19:51,780 --> 00:20:00,220
♪ Adakah kau dapat mengesan semua emosiku?♪

318
00:20:01,780 --> 00:20:05,620
♪ Perkara remeh pun boleh dikongsi sepanjang hari ♪

319
00:20:06,050 --> 00:20:09,889
♪ Kau pernah dengar semua lagu kegemaranku ♪

320
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:13,690
♪ Kisah dah sampai sini, hanya hampir ♪

321
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:16,070
♪ Berterus terang ♪

322
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:22,689
♪ Bolehkah kau meluahkan apa yang awak ingin katakan kepada aku?♪

323
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:26,000
♪ Biar impulsif mekar seperti bunga sakura ♪

324
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,190
♪ Hati melayang ♪

325
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:31,150
♪ Sedikit kelam-kabut, manis sehingga tak berdaya ♪

326
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:35,290
♪ Hampir saling memandang, kebahagiaan yang tak terduga ♪

327
00:20:35,620 --> 00:20:39,650
♪ Bolehkah kau beritahu aku jawapan yang dinanti-nantikan?♪

328
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:42,940
♪ Pandang aku, kau sengaja berdolak-dalik ♪

329
00:20:43,050 --> 00:20:44,370
♪ Seperti budak ♪

330
00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:48,360
♪ Apabila saling memandang lagi, langit berbintang bersinar terang ♪

331
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:54,910
♪ Masa berlalu dengan perlahan, tapi degupan jantung semakin laju ♪

